<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Chihowa okcha̱ya bilia yokʋt ƲIT52</title>
<time_sig>11.8.11.8.</time_sig>
<aka>The Awakened Sinner's Resolution</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chihowa okcha̱ya bilia yokʋt
 Auet anumpohonlishke;
 &quot;Sa nashuka yoka ish hoho̱yashke,&quot;
 Auet yak pim ahanchishke.

[C1]
   Chitokaka yʋt Chatan bok okhina
   Hoka chito chumi kia
   Oka nowʋt ant lhopulit aya hosh
   Saion tamaha ona tok

[V2]
 Chihowa ma! Chi nashuka hanta ya̱
 Hoho̱yot ahanta lashke;
 Chi Shilombish oka et is sama cha,
 Ik okcha̱ya, et ʋm ahni.

[C2]
   Chitokaka yʋt Chatan bok okhina
   Hoka chito chumi kia
   Oka nowʋt ant lhopulit aya hosh
   Saion tamaha ona tok

[V3]
 An Chihowa yʋt a̱ haiakakbano;
 Aiahnit hoho̱yo lishke;
 Hoyot issa lish falama li hokmʋt,
 Ilbʋshʋt sʋlli pulla chi̱.

[C3]
   Chitokaka yʋt Chatan bok okhina
   Hoka chito chumi kia
   Oka nowʋt ant lhopulit aya hosh
   Saion tamaha ona tok

[V4]
 Ithana li kʋt, onna hosh onnakma,
 Nishkin okchi mihinti hosh,
 Chisʋs a̱ nana im asilhha pullʋt
 Hoho̱yo la chi̱ mak oke.

[C4]
   Chitokaka yʋt Chatan bok okhina
   Hoka chito chumi kia
   Oka nowʋt ant lhopulit aya hosh
   Saion tamaha ona tok

[V5]
 Yakohmit im ilbʋsha li hoh kia,
 Sa haiyaklo keyukmʋno,
 Sai Okchalinchi iyi ituma ya̱
 Itu̱lʋt sʋlli pulla chi̱.

[C5]
   Chitokaka yʋt Chatan bok okhina
   Hoka chito chumi kia
   Oka nowʋt ant lhopulit aya hosh
   Saion tamaha ona tok

[V6]
 Chisʋs ma! yakohmit chi hoyo li ka,
 Ik illi, chik sʋm ahna hosh,
 Ik okcha̱ya, is sʋm ahna he bano,
 Ahnit chi hoho̱yo lishke.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>52</hymn_number>
<author>Alfred Wright</author>
</song>